# QX mod (this Git repository)

- **`VERSION`** (semver, one line) must match **`mod_version`** in **`gradle.properties`**.
- On meaningful changes: update **`CHANGELOG.md`**, bump **`VERSION`** / **`mod_version`**, **commit**, **`git push`**, annotated tag **`vX.Y.Z`**, **`git push origin vX.Y.Z`**.
- **Architectury repos:** CI must run both **`:fabric:build`** and **`:neoforge:build`**; release on **`v*`** should attach both JAR artifacts.
